idue and soil type. We conclude that both crop residue and SOM quality can affect the functional diversity of the soil microbial community, and that enzyme and Biolog analyses reflect complementary, but not inter-changeable, analyses. \textcopyright{} 2002 Elsevier Science Ltd. All rights reserved.},
