ibution patterns varied from year to year. We conclude that both rye and rye-vetch mixture can affect the functional diversity of soil microbial community but differences between them are marginal when compared to compost and no-compost treatments. Microbial communities were more responsive to compost applications than cover crop effects. ?? 2012 Elsevier B.V.},
